| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4572 — Recovery Inhibition (blackout)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 47449634-7bf0-556c-af1c-3818a7dc4f80"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
